name: NFTboxTz 04 💎📦
description:
Welcome to NFTboxTz 📦, where we release an NFT-filled grab bag with amazing, international artists. Each edition features 1 artist in particular for the core box concept. Each box is a low-priced 1/1 edition in comparison to the value of all the NFTs inside. 

This is a one-time, NFT grab bag that, once purchased, content will be sent to the buyer and detached. Then the box is empty and becomes a cool collectible itself.

💎 EDITION 04
🎨 3 pieces by Tù.úk'z
🎨 2 pieces by Alemac
🎨 1 piece by NFT Sizzle
🎨 1 piece by Guandanarian
🎨 1 piece by Jahipul
🎨 & the box itself by Fabi Yamada
